{"tid":782991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海軍商場出現裂痕　災難片前歹　香港人或又經歷未遇過的事","createTime":"2018-08-17T08:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T02:13:07.000Z","uid":47714,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e442242222a99813172d1d1610c9726651c68eda","tid":782991,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:08:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156466536282357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10156466536282357&d=pA37NK4D6xUPDCHRwULZb4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b95ea74e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156466536282357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：chenglap<br />\n<br />\n海軍商場出現裂痕這件事, 可以爆出很大鑊. 但市面的反應卻如此平靜.<br />\n<br />\n在灣仔與金鐘之間, 有一座樓出現裂痕, 然後大家卻沒有很注意, 這種劇情不就很像一些災難片前面階段的情節嗎? 如果是災難片的話, 這通常意味著在另外的地方, 隱藏更危險的東西.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃鵹: 話時話肯定大把二戰炸彈未爆<br />\n<br />\nEric KS Li: 可能是因為對海軍商場無什麼概念<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung: 很多香港人（包括我）一生中都未遇過這種事<br />\n<br />\nChan Sui Yin: 連要比咩反應都唔知， 講我自己， 剩低識share<br />\n<br />\nCyril Wong: 香港有大災難，會死得人多"},{"pid":"91d7eea9dc59899344b9f0615b1108c6067a1876","tid":782991,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T11:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0d3abd0ca037c13171acb369832e44d8e61105","tid":782991,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c16750da30884c50e967d5b55afec263c480cb3","tid":782991,"uid":106336,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:07:31.000Z","msg":"嗰度同荃灣線隧道距離幾遠？"},{"pid":"c64a16b6406378ec41f1c251d46f86d33418cf5a","tid":782991,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:54:10.000Z","msg":"沒事的"},{"pid":"ec0cf405df70b6b8754c02ec6f082e16593de099","tid":7